    "description": "Turn-based strategy roguelike ​game combining reverse minesweeper with inventory management. Collect items, organize inventory, mine for energy and vanquish your foes!<br><br>Gain new items and place them strategically in your ship. Each items have unique properties which may vary depending on their placement within the ship.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386800/extras/95d7a7a35ff48139dfced4ce3a118ccc.poster.avif?t=1748781729\" width=596 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386800/extras/95d7a7a35ff48139dfced4ce3a118ccc.webm?t=1748781729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386800/extras/95d7a7a35ff48139dfced4ce3a118ccc.mp4?t=1748781729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Efficiently mine to collect energy resources. Cells with numbers indicate the amount of energy available in their surrounding tiles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386800/extras/46ec672d5e30ded01038585a5506e789.poster.avif?t=1748781729\" width=596 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386800/extras/46ec672d5e30ded01038585a5506e789.webm?t=1748781729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386800/extras/46ec672d5e30ded01038585a5506e789.mp4?t=1748781729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your components to enhance your abilities and destroy the enemy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386800/extras/4328e1b51a2b63676b9ff9cb7c1f7e41.poster.avif?t=1748781729\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386800/extras/4328e1b51a2b63676b9ff9cb7c1f7e41.webm?t=1748781729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2386800/extras/4328e1b51a2b63676b9ff9cb7c1f7e41.mp4?t=1748781729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Enemy turns are triggered only during mining, which allows time to think of the next move.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Experiment with your strategies<br></li><li>More than 100 different items<br></li><li>3 different zones<br></li><li>Play endless mode</li></ul>",
